{"tid":2020425,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"外賣自取網站","createTime":"2020-05-17T05:05:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T07:25:19.000Z","uid":51143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"56fbcf9aa63e67247f036e809e1cc62bf7c712c6","tid":2020425,"uid":51143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T05:05:53.000Z","msg":"有冇需要做一個不收費的外賣自取網站？主要原因係想幫助餐廳減低支出。<br />\n<br />\n特點：<br />\n1）非牟利。<br />\n2）只提供配對服務，不處理付款及送餐。<br />\n3）有效防止有人濫用，如點餐後不取餐不付款。<br />\n<br />\n問題：<br />\n1）如何確認顧客身份？<br />\n2）如何處理顧客未有付款及取餐？<br />\n3）如何支付營運開支（如伺服器費用）？<br />\n<br />\n流程：<br />\n1）餐廳在網站登記及填寫餐單。<br />\n2）顧客在網站登記，需用電話號碼登記以作身份確認。<br />\n3）顧客在網站點餐。<br />\n4）餐廳收到訂單，預備食物。<br />\n5）顧客到餐廳取餐及付款。<br />\n6）餐廳在網站確認訂單完成。<br />\n7）如顧客未有付款及取餐，餐廳在網站回報。如沒有合理解釋及賠償餐廳損失，該顧客將不能再使用服務。"},{"pid":"a2a07060c801a3636dd1d743e98af064313a197b","tid":2020425,"uid":132174,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T05:31:42.000Z","msg":"我直接打電話去間餐廳度咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f7a449fc989c93988bb6199510850be3a7905dc","tid":2020425,"uid":260581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a2a07060c801a3636dd1d743e98af064313a197b","tid":2020425,"uid":132174,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T05:31:42.000Z","msg":"我直接打電話去間餐廳度咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T05:50:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"246e007d399f6ef47a060e6f53838c13bee2f8f5","tid":2020425,"uid":43924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a2a07060c801a3636dd1d743e98af06